  rico:history <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caHamilton%20Dibble%20Jessup%20%281806-1892%29%20was%20born%20in%20Augusta%20Township%2C%20and%20was%20educated%20at%20the%20Rev.%20John%20Bethune%27s%20grammar%20school%20at%20Augusta.%20In%201825%2C%20he%20was%20articled%20to%20William%20Caldwell%2C%20M.D.%20in%20Montreal%20as%20a%20student%20of%20medicine%2C%20and%20in%201829%20received%20his%20license%20to%20practice%20medicine%20in%20Upper%20Canada.%20In%201830%2C%20he%20was%20licensed%20to%20practice%20in%20Lower%20Canada.%20During%20the%20Rebellion%20of%201837%2C%20he%20was%20Captain%20of%20a%20company%20of%20militia%20under%20Colonel%20Young.%20In%201844%2C%20he%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20federal%20parliament%20for%20the%20county%20of%20Grenville%2C%20and%20retained%20the%20seat%20until%201847.%20He%20was%20also%20a%20Mayor%20of%20Prescott%2C%20and%20in%201867%20was%20appointed%20to%20the%20collectorship%20of%20customs%20at%20Prescott.>;
  rico:isOrWasDescribedBy <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.ca/KB/AuthorityRecord/Jessup%2C%20Hamilton%20Dibble%2C%201806-1892> .

