  auth:functionNote <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caThe%20Division%20of%20Surveys%20and%20Engineering%20conducted%20ground%20and%20aerial%20surveys%20of%20timber%2C%20land%20and%20water%20resources%2C%20the%20leasing%20of%20water%20power%20on%20Crown%20lands%20and%20the%20approval%20of%20plans%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20dams%20in%20Ontario.>;
