  rico:history <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caThe%20Division%20of%20Reforestation%20was%20created%20in%201941%20within%20the%20Ontario%20Department%20of%20Lands%20and%20Forests.%20It%20was%20created%20when%20the%20former%20Forestry%20Branch%20was%20divided%20into%20the%20Division%20of%20Forest%20Protection%2C%20Division%20of%20Air%20Services%20and%20Division%20of%20Reforestation.%20The%20division%20was%20known%20until%201942%20as%20the%20Division%20of%20Reforestation%20and%20Conservation.%20In%201957%2C%20the%20Division%20of%20Reforestation%20and%20the%20Division%20of%20Timber%20Management%20were%20merged%20to%20form%20the%20Division%20of%20Timber.>;
