  auth:functionNote <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caThe%20Forest%20Protection%20Branch%20was%20responsible%20for%20protecting%20Ontario%27s%20forests%20from%20fire%2C%20insects%20and%20disease.%20It%20also%20operated%20and%20maintained%20an%20aircraft%20fleet%20to%20meet%20the%20flying%20requirements%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Lands%20and%20Forests%20and%20other%20Departments%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Ontario.>;
