  rico:history <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caThe%20Land%20Management%20Division%20was%20created%20in%201971%20within%20the%20Department%20of%20Lands%20and%20Forests.%20It%20oversaw%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Branch%2C%20the%20Lands%20and%20Waters%20Branch%2C%20and%20the%20Surveys%20and%20the%20Engineering%20Branch.%20The%20division%20was%20eliminated%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Natural%20Resources%20on%20April%201%2C%201972.%20Within%20the%20new%20ministry%2C%20its%20functions%20were%20assumed%20by%20the%20Division%20of%20Lands%20and%20the%20Field%20Services%20Division.>;
