  rico:history <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caThe%20Office%20of%20the%20Provincial%20Municipal%20Auditor%20was%20established%20in%201897.%20The%20Auditor%20reported%20to%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20Ontario%20from%201897%20to%201914%2C%20and%20after%20that%20to%20the%20Provincial%20Secretary.%20The%20Provincial%20Municipal%20Auditor%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20newly%20created%20Bureau%20of%20Municipal%20Affairs%20in%201917.>;
