<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caClerks%20of%20the%20Peace%20were%20appointed%20to%20keep%20the%20county%20record%20and%20to%20assist%20the%20justices%20of%20the%20peace%20in%20quarter%20sessions%20in%20drawing%20indictments%2C%20entering%20judgements%2C%20issuing%20process%20etc.%2C%20and%20in%20administering%20business.%20Basic%20duties%20of%20the%20Clerks%20of%20the%20Peace%20included%3A%20recording%20forfeited%20estates%20of%20traitors%3B%20prosecuting%20negligent%20assessors%3B%20laying%20property%20assessment%20suits%20before%20Quarter%20Sessions%3B%20furnishing%20government%20with%20annual%20returns%20of%20assessed%20property%3B%20%20making%20writs%20of%20assessments%3B%20notifying%20parish%20and%20town%20officials%20to%20take%20oath%3B%20granting%20certificates%20of%20pardon%3B%20delivering%20jury%20lists%20to%20the%20Sheriff%3B%20recording%20marriages%3B%20transmitting%20to%20the%20government%20lists%20of%20licences%20granted%3B%20recording%20and%20transmitting%20to%20government%20lists%20of%20population%3B%20making%20up%2C%20yearly%2C%20a%20list%20of%20inhabitant%20householders%20and%20delivering%20it%20to%20the%20Sheriff%20for%20jurors%3B%20returning%20convictions%20to%20the%20General%20Quarter%20Session%20of%20the%20Peace%20and%20filing%20Justice%20of%20the%20Peace%27s%20Returns%20of%20Convictions%20and%20Returns%20of%20Finis%2C%20Penalties%20etc.%3B%20publishing%20the%20returns%20in%20the%20newspaper%20of%20the%20district%3B%20recording%20the%20place%20and%20time%20of%20sittings%20of%20the%20County%2FDistrict%20Court%3B%20and%20taking%20the%20affidavit%20of%20bastardy%20from%20unmarried%20mothers%20for%20support%20by%20declaring%20the%20father.>
  a owl:NamedIndividual .

