<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caCommunity%20Information%20Services%20was%20established%20in%201971%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Community%20Development%20Branch%20of%20the%20Ontario%20Department%20of%20the%20Provincial%20Secretary%20and%20Citizenship.%20The%20Community%20Information%20Services%20unit%20was%20%20transferred%20to%20the%20Ontario%20Ministry%20of%20Community%20and%20Social%20Services%20in%20April%201972%2C%20forming%20part%20of%20the%20Community%20Services%20Division.%20In%201974%2C%20however%2C%20the%20office%20became%20part%20of%20the%20Program%20Development%20Division.%20Effective%20April%201975%2C%20responsibility%20for%20the%20Community%20Information%20Services%20Office%20unit%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20Ontario%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%20and%20Recreation%2C%20where%20it%20formed%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Multicultural%20Development%20and%20Public%20Libraries%20Division.%20For%20a%20brief%20period%20in%201979%2C%20the%20unit%20formed%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Citizens%27%20Inquiry%20Branch%20of%20the%20Information%20Access%20Division.%20By%20December%201979%2C%20however%2C%20it%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20new%20Libraries%20and%20Community%20Information%20Branch.%20In%201989%2C%20responsibility%20for%20Community%20Information%20Services%20Program%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20Grants%20Administration%2C%20Planning%20and%20Evaluation%20Unit%2C%20of%20the%20Libraries%20and%20Community%20Information%20Branch.%20With%20this%20change%2C%20the%20Community%20Information%20Services%20unit%20ceased%20to%20exist.%20Ministerial%20responsibility%20for%20Community%20Information%20Services%20rested%20with%20the%20Ontario%20Department%20of%20the%20Provincial%20Secretary%2C%20from%201971%20to%201972%3B%20the%20Ontario%20Ministry%20of%20Community%20and%20Social%20Services%2C%20from%201972%20to%201975%3B%20the%20Ontario%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%20and%20Recreation%2C%20form%201975-%201982%3B%20the%20Ontario%20Ministry%20of%20Citizenship%20and%20Culture%2C%20from%201982-%201987%3B%20and%20with%20the%20Ontario%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%20and%20Communications%2C%20from%201987-1989.>
  a owl:NamedIndividual .

