<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caReita%20Margaret%20Grobb%20was%20born%20February%203%2C%201910%20to%20John%20Delbert%20Grobb%20and%20Leatha%20Tallman%20Grobb.%20She%20grew%20up%20on%20the%20Grobb%20family%20farm%20in%20Beamsville%20Ontario%2C%20before%20graduating%20from%20the%20Hamilton%20Normal%20School%20in%201932.%20She%20worked%20as%20a%20teacher%20for%20seven%20years%20before%20working%20as%20an%20accounting%20clerk%20in%20St.%20Catharines%20for%2025%20years.%20She%20retired%20to%20Grimsby%2C%20Ontario%2C%20and%20died%20April%208%2C%201988.>
  a owl:NamedIndividual .

