<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSelect%20Committees%20are%20ad-hoc%20committees%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20Ontario%20with%20specific%20terms%20of%20reference%20to%20investigate%20and%20report%20on%20a%20specific%20issue.%20This%20committee%20was%20initially%20established%20on%20April%2022%2C%201920%20with%20Henry%20Sloane%20Cooper%20as%20Chair%2C%20and%20was%20re-appointed%20on%20April%2028%2C%201921%20and%20March%2030%2C%201922.%20They%20issued%20their%20final%20report%20on%20February%2015%2C%201923.%20The%20committee%20recommended%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20cenotaph%20on%20University%20Avenue%20in%20Toronto%2C%20but%20recommended%20that%20it%20be%20postponed%20until%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20archives%20building%20at%20the%20same%20time.>
  a owl:NamedIndividual .

